{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbd9c485b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6350"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6350"},"text":"§ 6350.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Industrial insulation and audit guidelines","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd9c485c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6350/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Voluntary guidelines for energy efficiency auditing and insulating","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 18 months after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"October 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary, after consultation with utilities, major industrial energy consumers, and representatives of the insulation industry, shall establish voluntary guidelines for—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbd9c485d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6350/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the conduct of energy efficiency audits of industrial facilities to identify cost-effective opportunities to increase energy efficiency; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbd9c485e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6350/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the installation of insulation to achieve cost-effective increases in energy efficiency in industrial facilities.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd9c485f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6350/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Educational and technical assistance","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall conduct a program of educational and technical assistance to promote the use of the voluntary guidelines established under subsection (a).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbd9c4860-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/486/tI/s133"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–486, title I, § 133","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"Oct. 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/2840"},"text":"106 Stat. 2840","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/66/tI/s1052/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–66, title I, § 1052(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1995-12-21"},"text":"Dec. 21, 1995","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/109/717"},"text":"109 Stat. 717","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/362/tIV/s401/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–362, title IV, § 401(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/3282"},"text":"112 Stat. 3282","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbd9c4861-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbd9c4862-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbd9c4863-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Energy Policy Act of 1992, and not as part of the Energy Policy and Conservation Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbd9c4864-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/362"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–362","children":[],"tail":" struck out heading and text of subsec. (c). Text read as follows: “Not later than 2 years after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1995-10-24"},"text":"October 24, 1995","children":[],"tail":", and biennially thereafter, as part of the report required under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s6349/d"},"text":"section 6349(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary shall report to the Congress on activities conducted pursuant to this section, including—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(1) a review of the status of industrial energy auditing procedures; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) an evaluation of the effectiveness of the guidelines established under subsection (a) of this section and the responsiveness of the industrial sector to such guidelines.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1995—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/66"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–66","children":[],"tail":" in introductory provisions substituted “1995” for “1992”, and inserted “as part of the report required under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s6349/d"},"text":"section 6349(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":",” after “and biennially thereafter,”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
